title: American horror story murder house - Vivian & violet confronts ben/ ben dies
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: I never understood why any of the "good ghosts" didn't jump in and try to save Ben.
In AHS, if someone tells you that you're in danger, they mean you will die within 60 seconds.
A lot of people , if not almost everyone, die. Basically ending of every season.
The Harmon's. A very happy, but dead family.

I can’t be the only one that teared up a bit when they were decorating the tree? Yes they were happy (well not Tate and Haden) but they weren’t free, they were trapped for eternity. I especially felt for violet as she had her whole life ahead of her and now she’s literally house bound
